    dc:creator "Schaeffner, Bjoern C.; Beveridge, Ian" ;
    dc:date "2012" ;
    dc:title "Prochristianella Dollfus, 1946 (Trypanorhyncha: Eutetrarhynchidae) from elasmobranchs off Borneo and Australia, including new records and the description of four new species" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.208606>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.208608>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.208607> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.208606>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Prochristianella cairae n. sp. from Chiloscyllium punctatum (A – C, E) and C. indicum (D). A. Complete specimen. B. Bulb. C. Scolex. D. Mature segment. E. Gravid segment. Abbreviations: cs, cirrus sac; gc, gland-cells; mg, Mehlis’ gland; ov, ovary; rm, retractor muscle; t, testis; ut, uterus; vit, vitelline follicle." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/208606/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.208608>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Prochristianella cairae n. sp. from Chiloscyllium punctatum. Scanning electron micrographs. A. Scolex in dorsoventral view. B. Basal region, bothrial tentacular surface. C. Metabasal region, external tentacular surface. D. Lateral margin of bothrium, showing serrate spathulate spinitriches on proximal bothrial surface. E. Serrate spathulate spinitriches on pars vaginalis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/208608/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.208607>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Prochristianella cairae n. sp. from Chiloscyllium punctatum. Tentacular armature. A. Metabasal region, antibothrial surface. B. Metabasal region, bothrial surface; note opposing surface to (A) of the same tentacle. C. Distal region, internal surface. D. Basal region, external surface." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/208607/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

